When working in this repository, follow these rules.

## Required Context

Before making significant changes, review the following files:

1. `ai/prompts/system-prompt.md` — AI operating instructions
2. `ai/plans/current-sprint.md` — current development tasks
3. `ai/architecture/principles.md` — architecture rules

## Behaviour Expectations

- Follow the architecture defined in `ai/architecture`.
- Prefer small incremental changes.
- If requirements are unclear, ask for clarification rather than guessing.